{"tid":2065975,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"隔牆有耳： 善用科技抗爭 手足獲奧國藝術獎 - 李八方","createTime":"2020-06-16T03:16:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-16T03:16:38.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3fb734d5f173e0da467fb132bbbda1816bda044c","tid":2065975,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T03:16:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200616/4GQVDPROKAKBFWTKCWHB7SATL4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200616%2F4GQVDPROKAKBFWTKCWHB7SATL4%2F&d=UliE8fwpyfwMZiesMcCM7oV%2FGdaNkEJkjxlYCjQUfm8%3D&h=caac20d6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200616%2F4GQVDPROKAKBFWTKCWHB7SATL4%2F&h=01c2b64b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200616/4GQVDPROKAKBFWTKCWHB7SATL4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：<br />\n善用科技抗爭 手足獲奧國藝術獎 - 李八方<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XT2M3N7QRYE4IUY5MHLASECML4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXT2M3N7QRYE4IUY5MHLASECML4.gif&h=ecbe35c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n抗爭者透過蘋果AirDrop功能流動發佈文宣。受訪者提供圖片<br />\n<br />\n反送中抗暴之戰一直有賴唔少香港人打國際線，令外國人知香港發生乜事。有港人就搜集本地抗爭嘅科技應用，撰寫報告送去奧地利新媒體電子藝術中心參賽，結果奪得數碼藝術大獎入面「數碼社區」組別金獎，評審仲係首次將金獎頒畀匿名得獎者，就係「香港抗爭者」！<br />\n<br />\n報告由駐日香港藝術家蕭子文（Eric）同香港策展人鄺佳玲（Joel）編寫，叫「Be Water by Hong Kongers」，透過整理香港人喺抗爭中靈活運用科技，包括連登同Telegram、透過蘋果AirDrop發佈文宣、創作《願榮光歸香港》歌曲等，令評審大讚港人民主運動體現咗李小龍口中嘅「無形無狀」。<br />\n<br />\nEric知道獲獎後話，。。。。。。。。。。。。。，期望將香港抗爭藝術帶到世界巡迴展出。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}